{"tid":1261141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開槍英籍總警司拒答有否決定施放催淚彈 警呼喝：有需要打去PPRB","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:00:00.000Z","uid":80674,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6a74f84acc7475410613c81f0e1fff72fa2f7eb0","tid":1261141,"uid":80674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"[咁我打去英國啦屌你老母]<br />\n<br />\n民陣昨晚集會結束後，大批人士轉戰灣仔再包圍警察總部。警方今日凌晨開始清場，在6.12金鐘警民衝突中決定開槍的英籍總警司陶輝（Rupert Dover）亦再率領警員出動，驅散灣仔示威者。<br />\n<br />\n由傳媒在場拍攝的片段看到，陶輝昨日在現場現身，隨即被大批傳媒追問，6.12衝突警方有沒有使用過份武力，及是否由他決定向示威者施放催淚彈，但陶輝都沒有回答記者提問。在場有警員護送他離開，其間有記者繼續追訪，但被護送警員以交通安全為由推開，警員又呼喝：「有需要你打去PPRB」，並推開鏡頭阻止攝錄。最後陶輝在大批警員護送下返回警察總部。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59762374?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3_bUuKW79xbvTWCaIA2mpi2rUpFf454mc4oJoBe8mhuA8J0_lkVFhsoh0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59762374%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3_bUuKW79xbvTWCaIA2mpi2rUpFf454mc4oJoBe8mhuA8J0_lkVFhsoh0&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=1cb2cc9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F59762374%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3_bUuKW79xbvTWCaIA2mpi2rUpFf454mc4oJoBe8mhuA8J0_lkVFhsoh0&h=dce5f78d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190627/59762374?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3_bUuKW79xbvTWCaIA2mpi2rUpFf454mc4oJoBe8mhuA8J0_lkVFhsoh0</a>"},{"pid":"094b9c18aaa8824db1fbc0a4817a9f041b7fb9